graph TB
    subgraph "Notebook Controller Component"
        direction TB
        NotebookReconciler[Notebook Reconciler<br/>Main Controller]
        CullingReconciler[Culling Reconciler<br/>Idle Detection]
        MetricsCollector[Metrics Collector<br/>Prometheus Exporter<br/>8080/TCP]
        WebhookServer[Webhook Server<br/>CRD Conversion<br/>443/TCP - Disabled]
        HealthProbes[Health Probes<br/>8081/TCP]

        NotebookReconciler -.->|uses| MetricsCollector
        CullingReconciler -.->|uses| MetricsCollector
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resource Definitions"
        NotebookV1[Notebook v1<br/>Storage Version]
        NotebookV1beta1[Notebook v1beta1<br/>Beta API]
        NotebookV1alpha1[Notebook v1alpha1<br/>Legacy API]

        NotebookV1beta1 -.->|converts to| NotebookV1
        NotebookV1alpha1 -.->|converts to| NotebookV1
    end

    subgraph "Generated Resources"
        StatefulSet[StatefulSet<br/>Notebook Pod]
        Service[Service<br/>ClusterIP 80→8888]
        VirtualService[VirtualService<br/>Istio Routing]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraping]
        Istio[Istio Gateway<br/>Optional]
    end

    subgraph "Internal Dependencies"
        JupyterImages[Jupyter Notebook Images<br/>Container Runtime]
        JupyterHub[JupyterHub/ODH Dashboard<br/>Notebook Creation UI]
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| NotebookV1
    JupyterHub -->|creates via K8s API| NotebookV1

    NotebookV1 -->|watched by| NotebookReconciler
    NotebookReconciler -->|creates| StatefulSet
    NotebookReconciler -->|creates| Service
    NotebookReconciler -->|creates if USE_ISTIO| VirtualService

    NotebookReconciler -->|CRUD operations| K8sAPI
    CullingReconciler -->|queries /api/kernels| Service
    CullingReconciler -->|updates| NotebookV1

    StatefulSet -->|runs| JupyterImages
    VirtualService -.->|routes to| Istio

    Prometheus -->|scrapes| MetricsCollector

    WebhookServer -.->|disabled| NotebookV1beta1

    style NotebookReconciler fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style CullingReconciler fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style MetricsCollector fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style NotebookV1 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style StatefulSet fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Service fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style VirtualService fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style WebhookServer fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
